<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>68</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Adam suonte thim sala tang.
 A puidawk dingin kuoa hung ding?
 A gimtheih nau hung thawkpih ding leh,
 Amau sika thi di'n,
 Van Lal cha A hung pieng.

[V2]
 Hallelujah lawpin kipak hitiu,
 Van Lal Jubili chu;
 Bethlehem leh kalvari tang chung ah,
 Pawtna dak a gi tai.

[V3]
 2. Sheol nuoia Mansawl khawpi,
 Pawtna dak hunggi chu na zau em?
 Nang u dingin van Lal cha ngei chu,
 Thisana kithuom in,
 Melma khawpi A sim.

[V4]
 3. Nunglam melma gal a tho ui,
 Gitlohna'n tha a zakkhum mat guon;
 &quot;Jeho-Jire tang&quot; ah hung kai in,
 &quot;Hossana&quot; hun chawiin,
 Salem puonzak nuoiah.

[V5]
 4. Salem puonzak nuoia bitna,
 Salem Lalpa khuta vangpiekna;
 Jeho-Jire tanga umhaw chu,
 Hung chang ngei ding ahiu,
 Hallelujah Amen.</lyrics>
<title>Suohchakna Jubili</title>
</song>